N'agbata afọ N’agbata afọ 1924 na 1956, e wepụtara mkpụrụ ego a ga-eji na Togo
Kemgbe 1945, Togo na-eji franc West African CFA.
N'agbata afọ 1884 na 1914, akara Germany bụ ego nke Togo dịka Germany bụ ike ọchịchị
N'afọ 1914, ndị agha Britain na France weghaara Togo
E kewara Togo n'ime mpaghara abụọ nke Njikọ Mba, ebe ọdịda anyanwụ, akụkụ Britain nabatara pound British West Africa ma mesịa bụrụ akụkụ nke Ghana
N'ebe ọwụwa anyanwụ, n'ókèala France, a nabatara franc French, gbakwunyere na 1924 site na mkpụrụ ego e wepụtara n'aha Mandate Territory of Togo
A na-emepụta mkpụrụ ego ndị a ruo n'oge ruo n'afọ 1956 ma na-ekesa ya na franc CFA site na 1945
Ọ dịghị mkpụrụ ego a na-ekesa kpọmkwem na Togo kemgbe 1956, ọ bụ ezie na mkpụrụ ego 1957 nke French West Africa nwekwara aha Togo.
N'afọ 1924, e webatara aluminium-bronze 50 centimes, franc 1 na 2, bụ́ nke e dekwasịrị aha franc ọzọ na 1925 na centimes 50 ahụ kụrụ afọ n'ala ruo 1926
N'afọ 1948, e wepụtara mkpụrụ ego aluminom 1 na franc 2, bụ́ nke a na-emepụtakwa aluminium-bronze
